@startuml
title Rendering - Level 1

skinparam ParticipantPadding 8

participant "Widget" as Widget
participant "Sparkle" as Sparkle
participant "Screen" as Screen

Widget -> Sparkle : describes what to draw
Sparkle -> Sparkle : prepares drawing commands
Sparkle -> Screen : shows the frame

note over Widget,Screen
Widgets do not draw directly to the screen.
They describe drawing work via RenderUnit,
and Sparkle performs it during the render
step.
end note

@enduml
